dmca.title: Convert-me site claims unauthorized text conversion
dmca.body:
1.	The copyrighted work at issue is the text that appears on http://www convert-me.com/ web site including the root page and over 1,000 other pages in both English and Russian versions of the site (http://www.convert-me.com/en and http://www.convert-me.com/ru respectively).

2.	The material I claim is infringing the copyrighted work listed in item #1 above is the following web search result(s):

Search Query:	pressure, speed, temperature, time, torque 
Infringing Web Pages: convertplus.com/en/

The query "site : convertplus.com" returns the list of all indexed pages of the web site that infringes the copyright of the item #1 above.

3.	My email address is [private]@convert
